This paper deals with learning from expert demonstrations in artificial intelligence and machine learning, which is a common topic in the cs.AI sub-category. The paper also discusses the use of Markov decision processes, which is a common topic in the cs.LG and cs.RO sub-categories. The paper also mentions formal methods and specifications, which are topics in the cs.PL and cs.SY sub-categories. Therefore, the most likely sub-categories are cs.AI, cs.LG, cs.RO, cs.SY, and cs.PL, in that order.
